Prerequisites:
--------------

Building libplaysound from a distributed tarball requires GObject, GIO,
libcanberra, and (optionally) Gtk3 development headers to be installed.

Building from a Git checkout additionally requires the Vala compiler and the
libcanberra Vala bindings to be installed.

